verbose_text: To identify and quantify the proteins (the " prey ") that associate with PD-1-OST molecules (the " bait ") over the course of pervanadate stimulation, we applied our SWATH (sequential window acquisition of all theoretical fragment ion spectra)-MS workflow to PD-1 OST CD4 + T cells that were briefly expanded to induce high levels of PD-1 and then treated for 2, 5, or 15 min with pervanadate or left untreated.
